0.1.4 (2008/03/09)
   Use CMake build system.

0.1.3 (2007/10/29)
   Support for -fvisibility=hidden

0.1.2 (2007/10/09)
   Properly handle situation where _setsize() requests
    shrinking packet (=some data or dma is already written
    over requested size).

0.1.1 (2007/10/07)
   clean up packet even if buffer is in cancelled state

0.1.0 (2007/10/06)
   proper documentation and Doxyfile

0.0.13 (2007/10/02)
   improved Makefile
   gentoo ebuild

0.0.12 (2007/09/30)
   another _cancel() bugfix
   _reserve() -related cleanup

0.0.11 (2007/09/29)
   better fake dma implementation

0.0.10 (2007/09/21)
   bugfixes

0.0.9 (2007/09/18)
   ps_packet_cancel() fix

0.0.8 (2007/09/17)
   fixed some incorrect packet size problems

0.0.7 (2007/09/14)
   PS_PACKET_TRY flag, returns EBUSY if can't proceed without waiting
   ps_packet_cancel()

0.0.6 (2007/09/09)
   new example application 'texec'
   _dma() API change
   some bugfixes in _dma()

0.0.5 (2007/09/03)
   rewritten _reserve(), fixes possible (?) bug
   some API improvements and code cleanups

0.0.4 (2007/09/02)
   some cleanups
   compiles with -ansi flag

0.0.3 (2007/08/31)
   shm support rewritten (previous version had severe design error)

0.0.2 (2007/08/30)
   shm support
   lots of API rework / cleanup
   new example application 'shmchat'

0.0.1 (2007/08/27)
   initial release
